Special report by Saskia Wishart of NOT FOR SALE - an international anti-slavery movement. Did you know there are 30,000,000 slaves worldwide...the majority being women and children? No country is spared. From the USA to the slums of Asia the scourge of humanity is fast becoming the most lucrative business. Children, as young as a few years, usually girls, are sold into slavery...read all about this and how you too can help in many ways!
